de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class SubprojectInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.SubprojectInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, IInfo, IProjectRelation, Serializable, Comparable<SubprojectInfo>

    public class SubprojectInfo
extends ErpsData
implements IInfo, IProjectRelation, Comparable<SubprojectInfo>
    The light version of the subproject with only important informations. The class contains only required subproject informations to show a subproject in the browser tree.
